dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. "707320 3-86." Shipping list no.: 1990-0342-P. Map shows UNDOF zones, built-up areas, Israeli settlements, refugee camps, razed villages, international boundaries, five classes of roads, railroads. Map also shows: Israel-Lebanon/Syria Armistice Line and limit of Demilitarized Zone as of July 20, 1949 ; Syrian village--name and location in the Israeli-occupied Golan Heights taken from pre-1967 sources. UTM grid: Zone 36.
